Sentencas: Dense samarium doped ceria (SDC) thin films are deposited using electrostatic spray deposition (ESD) technique.
Titulo: Investigation of nozzle shape effect on Sm0.1Ce0.9O1.95 thin film prepared by electrostatic spray deposition

Sentencas: The influences of nozzle shape on the distribution of liquid jet at the nozzle tip and the morphology of the deposited SDC films are elucidated.
Titulo: Investigation of nozzle shape effect on Sm0.1Ce0.9O1.95 thin film prepared by electrostatic spray deposition

Sentencas: Geometries of three nozzles employed are flat, sawtooth and wedge tips.
Titulo: Investigation of nozzle shape effect on Sm0.1Ce0.9O1.95 thin film prepared by electrostatic spray deposition

Sentencas: From the observation of jet formation, the nozzle in flat shape gives the highest distribution of emitted droplets.
Titulo: Investigation of nozzle shape effect on Sm0.1Ce0.9O1.95 thin film prepared by electrostatic spray deposition

Sentencas: The deposited films are characterized using a combination of XRD, SEM and AFM techniques.
Titulo: Investigation of nozzle shape effect on Sm0.1Ce0.9O1.95 thin film prepared by electrostatic spray deposition

Sentencas: XRD results reveal that the single-phase fluorite structure forms at a relatively low deposition temperature of 400 degrees C.
Titulo: Investigation of nozzle shape effect on Sm0.1Ce0.9O1.95 thin film prepared by electrostatic spray deposition

Sentencas: The flat spray tip provides the most uniform and smooth thin films, and also presents the lowest agglomeration of particles on thin-film surface.
Titulo: Investigation of nozzle shape effect on Sm0.1Ce0.9O1.95 thin film prepared by electrostatic spray deposition
